self.title: CDISC Questionnaire IIEF Test Code Terminology

definition: International Index of Erectile Function test code.
name: International Index of Erectile Function Questionnaire Test Code
preferredTerm: CDISC Questionnaire IIEF Test Code Terminology
synonyms: International Index of Erectile Function Questionnaire Test Code

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how often were you able to get an erection during sexual activity?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Able to Get an Erection During Sexual Activity

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks when you had erections with sexual stimulation, how often were your erections hard enough for penetration?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Erections Hard Enough for Penetration

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks when you attempted sexual intercourse, how often were you able to penetrate (enter) your partner?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Able to Penetrate Your Partner

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks during sexual intercourse, how often were you able to maintain your erection after you had penetrated (entered) your partner?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Able to Maintain Your Erection After You Had Penetrated Your Partner

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks during sexual intercourse, how difficult was it to maintain your erection to completion of intercourse?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Maintain Your Erection to Completion of Intercourse

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how many times have you attempted sexual intercourse?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - How Many Times Have You Attempted Sexual Intercourse

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks when you attempted sexual intercourse, how often was it satisfactory for you?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - How Often was it Satisfactory for You

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how much have you enjoyed sexual intercourse?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - How Much Have You Enjoyed Sexual Intercourse

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks when you had sexual stimulation or intercourse, how often did you ejaculate?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - How Often Did You Ejaculate

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks when you had sexual stimulation or intercourse, how often did you have the feeling of orgasm with our without ejaculation?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Did You Have Feeling of Orgasm With or Without Ejaculation
synonyms: IIEF01-Did You Have Feeling of Orgasm

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how often have you felt sexual desire?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - How Often Have You Felt Sexual Desire

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how would you rate your level of sexual desire?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Rate Your Level of Sexual Desire
synonyms: IIEF01-Rate Your Level of Sexual Desire

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how satisfied have you been with your overall sex life?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Satisfied with Overall Sex Life

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how satisfied have you been with your sexual relationship with your partner?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Satisfied with Your Sexual Relationship with Your Partner

terms.definition: International Index of Erectile Function - Over the past four weeks how do you rate your confidence that you could get and keep an erection?
terms.preferredTerm: IIEF - Your Confidence to Get and Keep an Erection
